{
  "message": "test(fuzz): add 34 text_parsing corpus seeds\n\nCovers fromfile_text and fromstring parsing edge cases:\n- Separator variants: space, comma, tab, semicolon, newline, double-space\n- Numeric formats: ints, floats, scientific notation (1.5e10, 2.3e-5)\n- Special floats: inf, -inf, nan (both cases)\n- Boundary values: max/min i64, max u64, u8 boundary, max/min f64\n- Format variants: leading dot (.5), trailing dot (1.), plus sign (+1)\n- Alternative bases: hex (0x10), octal (0o10), binary (0b101)\n- Multi-line matrix formats\n- Edge cases: empty, single value, zeros, extra whitespace\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
